---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About the Impeachment Tracker — helping citizens make their voices heard.">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about">
      <h1>About This Site</h1>

      <p>
        Democracy works best when representatives hear from the people they serve.
        I know that engaging can be difficult, so this site exists for one simple reason: 
        to make it easier for you to find out where your elected officials stand on impeachment,
        and provide contact info and and a sample script to contact them directly 
        with your opinion. Thanks to <a href="https://5calls.org">5calls.org</a> for the inspiration.
      </p>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Find your rep</strong> on the map or search by state</li>
        <li><strong>See where they stand</strong> based on public statements, votes, and co-sponsorships</li>
        <li><strong>Call them</strong> using the phone number and sample script on their page</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Sources</h2>

      <p>
        Stance classifications are based on public records including congressional votes,
        bill co-sponsorships, official press releases, and news reporting. Member contact
        information comes from the <a href="https://github.com/unitedstates/congress-legislators" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@unitedstates/congress-legislators</a>
        project and official government sources.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you believe a stance classification is incorrect, please
        <a href="https://github.com/djfeldman94/impeach-tracker/issues/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">open an issue</a>
        with a source and I'll update it.
      </p>

      <h2>Open Source</h2>

      <p>
        This project is fully open source. View the code, suggest improvements, or
        report issues on <a href="https://github.com/djfeldman94/impeach-tracker" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about li {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding-left: 1.5em;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .about li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
